  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a hardcore tower defense enthusiast, I set out to create a non-traditional roguelike tower defense game. Endless Tower Defense: Survive is a game I developed over two months using the 『CliCli』. If you're interested in discussing, providing feedback, or just having a laugh, feel free to join our QQ group: 907832371.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/50a7b17fc6cfc62af20668fa74f75141.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Intense Mowing Action, Ultimate Stress Relief</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No need for rapid operations – just click to enjoy the idle roguelike fun. Face endless waves of monsters, equip weapons, upgrade the tower soul to harvest the horde, and gather resources to upgrade your tower and soul. Dual-wield your tower and soul to defeat bosses and experience the ultimate thrill of endless mowing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/c5d4350cce18ecb40860827dae8b9394.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Variety and Depth, Never Gets Boring</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With nearly a hundred unique weapons and upgrade effects, enjoy the thrill of mowing down enemies while stacking top-tier roguelike experiences, ensuring each battle delivers double the excitement. Balance your weapon combinations and upgrade effects to optimize offense and defense, allowing for infinite mowing and stress relief.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/9c771b82e3dd13e88ed7014ee0b7acd1.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tower and Soul Synergy, United We Stand</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abyss to gather soul stones and enhance your tower soul for combat assistance. Whether dual-wielding with separate attack paths or merging them into the ultimate defense tower, you'll experience the ultimate mowing thrill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/764380ec1570c430cba1a122b52d0580.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adapt and Conquer, Master the Elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Against different enemies, remember the counter rules: Metal crushes medium armor; Piercing counters light armor; Magic defeats heavy armor; Siege breaks reinforced armor; Chaos weapons treat all equally, ignoring armor! Use the right weapon to mow down enemies faster and more efficiently!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.poster.avif?t=1737625524\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.webm?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303150/extras/d3c893fb6b9cf2b514066df639876cc7.mp4?t=1737625524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
